column5: Lets have anyone needing this done make a post here. Put in your username now (the one you log in with) and how many posts you had at proboards. As we get to them we will delete your response. We do need you to check your old post count though. It may take awhile. There is no prize for first place.
Post count carry over from pro boards  Blake    posts
Lots, but who gives a (insert smilie for rats ass here) ? I'm startin' over!
setomonkey 99,056. Oh wait, you're going to check the old board...    Mike
